OL,3,CDisposable vapes banned in Wales
OL,5,FDisposable vapes are now banned in
OL,6,FWales.
OL,8,FThe new law - which is in place across
OL,9,Fthe UK - came into effect 1 June and
OL,10,Fwill prohibit the sale of single use
OL,11,Fvapes.
OL,13,FThe law will be applied to businesses
OL,14,Fnot individuals, meaning that it will
OL,15,Fbe a criminal offence to sell or
OL,16,Fsupply disposable vapes but it will
OL,17,Fnot be illegal for people to use them
OL,18,Ffor personal use.
