OL,3,CDisposable vapes banned in Wales
OL,5,FThe Welsh Government says the ban has
OL,6,Fbeen introduced to reduce the
OL,7,Fenvironmental harm caused by their
OL,8,Fproduction and incorrect disposal.
OL,10,FEnvironmental charity Keep Wales Tidy
OL,11,Festimates that over just one year,
OL,12,F360,000 single use vapes are littered
OL,13,Fon the ground in Wales, while 120,000
OL,14,Fare flushed down the toilet.
OL,16,FRogue traders who continue to sell
OL,17,Fthem risk a fine of #200 in the first
OL,18,Finstance, followed by an unlimited
OL,19,Ffine or jail time for repeat offending.
