OL,3,CDisposable vapes banned in Wales
OL,5,FPublic Health Wales has welcomed the
OL,6,Fban.
OL,8,FThe health body says that there is a
OL,9,F"clear consensus" among health experts
OL,10,Fthat the availability and marketing of
OL,11,Fdisposable vape products has driven a
OL,12,Fsignificant rise in vaping among
OL,13,Fchildren and young people.
OL,15,FThey say around 16% of year eleven
OL,16,Fpupils regularly use vapes and nearly
OL,17,Fhalf have tried vaping. Of these, most
OL,18,Fhad never smoked before taking up
OL,19,Fvaping.
