OL,3,CDisposable vapes banned in Wales
OL,5,FWhile the majority of single-use vapes
OL,6,Fcontain nicotine, the ban will also
OL,7,Fapply to nicotine free disposable
OL,8,Fvapes.
OL,10,FVapes now need to be refillable,
OL,11,Frechargeable, and have a replaceable
OL,12,Fcoil.
OL,14,FDeputy First Minister, with
OL,15,Fresponsibility for Climate Change, Huw
OL,16,FIrranca-Davies said: "Single-use vapes
OL,17,Fcreate litter and plastic pollution;
OL,18,Fthis ban will help stop the serious
OL,19,Fharm these products cause to our
OL,20,Fwildlife and environment.
