OL,3,CDisposable vapes banned in Wales
OL,5,F"They should be recycled at a vape
OL,6,Fshop, or taken to a local authority
OL,7,Frecycling centre, to be disposed of
OL,8,Fsafely. Vapes should never go in the
OL,9,Fbin as they are susceptible to
OL,10,Fcatching fire."
OL,12,FMinister for Mental Health and
OL,13,FWellbeing, Sarah Murphy added: "In
OL,14,Faddition to the environmental impacts,
OL,15,Fwe know single-use vapes are being
OL,16,Fused by children and young people and
OL,17,Fare a factor in the significant
OL,18,Fincreases in youth vaping that we have
OL,19,Fseen in recent years.
